  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I also gave a talk about that [LAUGHS] to various organizations, one of which is that there was a, a, a, big concern that the moon-- and particularly espoused by one scientist-- that the moon had a, a layer of 15 to 20 feet of fine dust.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this man said, you, you can't send people to the moon because they'll get swallowed up by this dust layer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we sent the surveyors up to find out if that was the case.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The moon is-- insofar as the solidity of the surface, is just like Earth, except it doesn't have any water.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so we, we sent the five that were successful, showed that it was OK to send men there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that kind of was the precursor to the Apollo program.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we know what happened on the Apollo program.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We sent men to the moon, and it was highly successful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that really was the start of my career in, in rocket propulsion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I'm in quotes told I'm a 'rocket scientist.' [LAUGHS] And a lot of people get a kick out a calling me a rocket scientist, but I-- I guess I am in, in some way.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "After that program, I, I was assigned to what was called Mariner, the Mariner Mars 71.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we sent a spacecraft to orbit Mars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was launched aboard an Atlas-Centaur launch vehicle, one of which failed and plunked our spacecraft into the ocean.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But the other one got there OK and orbited Mars and, and photographed about 80% of the surface of Mars.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, and that told us a lot about one of our sister planets.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
